Role: ssl_role
=========

Automatic the process of obtaining ssl cert with letsencrypt.

Requirements
------------
Server: EC2 OPENVPN instance with aws_policy.xml enabled


Role Variables
--------------

host = domain name
email = This email will be linked to the ssl cert
ssl_test= {dns, html}  Chose challenge type. html requires port 80 to be open


Dependencies
------------


Example Playbook
----------------

Example: ansile-playbook test.yml -e host=ababio.com -e email=michaelkwasi@gmail.com -e ssl_test=dns

Author Information
------------------

An optional section for the role authors to include contact information, or a website (HTML is not allowed).
